• 'do' does nothing on grass/water - move to find resources
• Craft progression: wood → table → wood_pickaxe → stone → stone_pickaxe → iron tools
• Sleep when energy low to restore and unlock wake_up achievement

Choose 1-5 actions to execute in sequence. Focus on exploring to find resources and crafting tools to unlock achievements.
